channel.title: Error decompiling
channel.description:
Hey guys, i need some help here, im trying to decompile a class file since i lost the java, im using DJ's decompiler but it drops an error saying "the file is too large", is there any other program i can use to decompile it? or anyone interested in helping me out with it.?
